  "title": "Japanese Language Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 407914]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Teach Japanese as a foreign language to working adults in an immersive classroom environment</li><li>Deliver lessons using the direct method to encourage natural communication in Japanese</li><li>Promote cultural exchange and introduce Japanese customs and traditions</li><li>Enable students to achieve practical communication skills for personal and professional use</li><li>Participate in lesson planning and contribute to school-related tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Possess one of the following qualifications:Degree major or sub-major in Japanese Language TeachingCompletion of a Japanese Teacher Training Course at an accredited institutionPassed the Japanese Language Teaching Competency Test</li><li><strong>Proficiency in Japanese to conduct Japanese lessons </strong></li><li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Ability to work collaboratively as a team player</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference:</p><p>https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p><strong>EA Personnel Name:</strong></p><p>Kota Baba</p><p><strong>EA Personnel Reg. no.:</strong></p><p>R22106801</p><p><strong>EA License no.:</strong></p><p>07C5771</p>",
